::THe Galactors/Zardus/Autofire::

Two shots from Composer whiz by Autofire, as well as a missile from
Zardus. Zardus's second missile hits him, and he begins to feel his
energy draining quickly. Autofire growls, loosing altitude. His energy
levels begin to recharge as soon as he's out of the draining field.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Supernova scans behind himself, seeing Autofire off his tail. His
scanners also detect Abominus forming.

"Form Galaxor!" he orders his team, the jet that comprised him, Scrap,
and Slasys splitting into seperate bots, the other jet flying for a
little while and then splitting up as well. The bots fall toward the
ground, transforming into bodyparts and combining on the way.

Galaxor lands on the ground, making it shake with his weight. He looks
ahead at Abominus, lifting the large missile launcher that was in his
hand and firing two missiles at the other Gestalt.
